dc_title_s: Series of riparian maps featuring the Newark coastline along the Passaic River, from the Morris Canal to the Mt. Pleasant Cemetery, 1859-1890
dc_description_s: Series of riparian maps featuring the Newark coastline along the Passaic River, from the Morris Canal to the Mt. Pleasant Cemetery|Source map supplied by New Jersey Department of Environmental Protection|Dates on sheets range from 3-1859, 1-1879, 1-1890 and one with no date given
